Donald P. Zerio 
Executive Compensation
As Vice President, Finance and Chief Financial Officer at LINEAR TECHNOLOGY CORP, Donald P. Zerio  made $1,298,280 in total compensation.  Of this total $305,327 was received as a salary, $515,851 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $409,800 was awarded as stock and $67,302 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


